| Bollinger range fade | Bollinger 20,2, RSI2, ADX14, EMA50, ATR14 | M5 regime, M1 trigger | Signal extreme + ATR + spread floor | Bollinger midline | 1:0.8ŌĆō1.3 | 0.25ŌĆō0.40 |
| Donchian volatility breakout | ADX14, Donchian 20, ATR14, MACD | M5 regime, M1 trigger | Breakout-bar low/high or 1.0├ŚATR | Fixed 1.8R | 1:1.8 | 0.35ŌĆō0.60 |
